Weldon Forbes JORGENSEN, Appellant, v. E. B. SWOPE, Warden, United States Penitentiary, McNeil Island, Washington, Appellee. No. 9466. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. March 7, 1940. Weldon Forbes Jorgensen in pro. per. No other appearance entered.

Before WILBUR, GARRECHT, and DENMAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Petition for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted.
